Lucille Hutton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucille_Hutton 0 Lucille Hutton (1899 – 1970) was an American film actress of the silent era. She appeared in 56 films between 1916 and 1931. She was born in Indiana. Lucille_Hutton ( 1899 – 1970 ) was an_American_film_actress of the_silent_era . She appeared in 56_films between 1916_and_1931 . She was_born in Indiana .
